<img src="http://www.bizcommunity.com/c/1804/437269.jpg" alt="nlighten and MANGO-OMC join forces" width="420" height="133">The nlighten team works with high-performing companies offering the full array of services required to design, develop and deliver exceptional customer experiences for a wide range of business types.Nathalie Schooling, CEO of nlighten, says: "We have a wealth of information about the very important and rapidly evolving topic of customer experience and we have partnered with MANGO-OMC to make it accessible across multiple platforms. We look forward to sharing our data and successes with businesses, organisations and brands." Nicole Capper, agency owner and MD, says: "We love to partner with extraordinary organisations and thoroughly look forward to working with nlighten."